			<div class="content" id="post-content-3713566">
									

<p>This is my entry for the first round of Jam-Con 2018!</p>
<p>Thanks to: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518919599" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;">Tanhony</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518919599" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zogip2" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3209195); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3209195&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518919599" alt="Zogip2" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3209195)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zogip2" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3209195); return false;">Zogip2</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilas-crowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518919599" alt="Xilas Crowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilas-crowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;">Xilas Crowe</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grimmcreeper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2843467); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2843467&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518919599" alt="GrimmCreeper" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2843467)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grimmcreeper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2843467); return false;">GrimmCreeper</a></span> for looking this over.</p>
<p>Also thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518919599" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;">PeppersGhost</a></span> for some help during the brainstorming process.</p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Attribution:</span></strong><br />
- <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:55_-_Bogota_-_D%C3%A9cembre_2008.JPG">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:55_-_Bogota_-_Décembre_2008.JPG</a> (Credit to Martin St-Amant - Wikipedia, photo is under CC-BY-SA-3.0)<br />
- UIU photo comes from the UIU Hub page. It is unattributed there, but was uploaded by Drewbear. Presumably, it is CC compliant, but I do not have an exact source.</p>
<hr />
<p>If you liked this thing and would like to read some comments about it, or check out other things I've written, head to <a href="/stormbreath">my author page</a> for more!</p>

