														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3720600">
									

<p>No one will notice if there is no one around to notice.</p>
<p>In all seriousness, I feel that this is a UIU document that actually gives the UIU some of the FBI flavor the more fantasy/sci-fi delves the GoI take lack. Additionally, placing them against a Chicago Spirit super-cleaner makes for a compelling antagonist.</p>
<p>I'd say others interested in UIU GoI formats should take note, for this is certainly a good way to keep things grounded.</p>
<p>+1.</p>

